The Oblitercons/Minion/Sixshot/Unitron/Demon Wulf/Dark Claw/Flesh 
Ripper/Serpentor/Shockwave:


Dark One fired off another two missiles at the Mafia Base.

---

Breakdown switched the setting of the grenade to have no time delay, firing 
off another grenade at Shokaract from his launcher.

---

Pyro laughed, firing off a single fire ball at the grenade, watching it 
explode before it even got to him.

---

Hiss fired off three fusion blasts at Shokaract.

---

Scavenger fired off 25 explosive shells at the Mafia Base, raising his left 
arm, firing off a rocket at the base from his missile launcher.

---

Demon Wulf fired off a blade missile at the Mafia Base.

---

Flesh Ripper fired off 10 rapid optic blasts at Shokaract.

---

Dark Claw formed another large orb, throwing the orb at the Mafia Base.

---

Unitron barrel rolled, taking shot hits to his wings.  He fired off two more 
missiles at the Mafia Base.

---

Sixshot get hit by Shockwave's missile, crashing to the ground.
